; Tests for item.cc: get_comment paths
; Covers: (return from get_comment)
;         (no note returns empty string)
;         (note formatting with newlines)

2024/01/01 No Note
    Expenses:Food  $10
    Assets

2024/01/02 Short Note
    Expenses:Gas  $20  ; tiny
    Assets

; get_comment returns both empty and non-empty for different postings
; Exercises (no note) and (short note)
test reg Expenses --format '%(comment)\n'

  ; tiny
end test
